y follow people who litter. They always belch poison gas."},{"version":"x","text":"The combination of garbage bags and industrial waste caused the chemical reaction that created this Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"y","text":"Inhaling the gas they belch will make you sleep for a week. They prefer unsanitary places."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"The combination of garbage bags and industrial waste caused the chemical reaction that created this Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Inhaling the gas they belch will make you sleep for a week. They prefer unsanitary places."},{"version":"sun","text":"Unsanitary places are what they like best. They can be spotted in Alola, often with Grimer in hot pursuit."},{"version":"moon","text":"It gorges on trash until its stomach is full. Then it belches toxic gas. An unlucky whiff of gas will put a person in the hospital."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Poisonous gas leaks out of it when it breathes. Muk that catch a whiff of that stench will come drooling."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"If a young Pok\u00e9mon or child breathes in the toxic gas that Trubbish belches out, it could be a life-threatening situation."},{"version":"sword","text":"Its favorite places are unsanitary ones. If you leave trash lying around, you could even find one of these Pok\u00e9mon living in your room."},{"version":"shield","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon was born from a bag stuffed with trash. Galarian Weezing relish the fumes belched by Trubbish."}],"evo":{"name":"trubbish","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"garbodor","level":1,"min_level":36,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happ